      • convertArrayToSet

        public static <T> Set<T> convertArrayToSet(T[] array)
        Utility function that converts an array into a set. Doubled elements as well as null values will be removed.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the generic type of the array
        Parameters:
        array - the array to convert
        Returns:
        the set containing all elements of passed array, doubled elements will just appear once in returned Set.
